Package it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.controller

Interface Controller

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LedgerMenuController
    public interface Controller
    This interface is implemented by all the classes that have the responsibility to act as a bridge between the view and the model of the application.
    Author:
    Tommaso Catervi
